precious and irreplaceable.

513
00:41:39,300 --> 00:41:41,480
What a bother!

514
00:41:41,480 --> 00:41:44,780
You should pay 1900yen to me,
or else, I would never forgive you!

515
00:41:44,780 --> 00:41:46,920
Because of you, he runs away!

516
00:41:47,000 --> 00:41:48,240
Stupid!

517
00:41:48,240 --> 00:41:51,900
Because of that fate,
I met her that day.

518
00:41:51,900 --> 00:41:53,960
It has been 7 years, huh?

519
00:42:00,980 --> 00:42:03,980
An encounter can change someone.

520
00:42:09,970 --> 00:42:13,960
If people from the future live in this era..

521
00:42:13,960 --> 00:42:16,460
They are going to die?

522
00:42:16,460 --> 00:42:20,950
