lived for 3 years in this era.

523
00:42:20,950 --> 00:42:22,780
So, break up with Mihane-chan
and go back to the future!

524
00:42:22,780 --> 00:42:24,780
For the sake of you both.

525
00:42:25,010 --> 00:42:28,960
Miura-san, do you still want to live here?

526
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:33,460
I don't mind to die, because I have a family
that is more precious than my life here.

527
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:37,960
